Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你要睡到什麼時候啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然破壞約定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是等了一整個晚上喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我等的不耐煩時  已經是早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我聽好  我非常非常地生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有聽懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我約會的話就原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是待在房間裡面太不健康了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難想像是吸血鬼會說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直想約會一次看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到剛剛為止明明還那麼生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會那麼生氣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在問你這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是你對每個人都很溫柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我優柔寡斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻偏偏對我很冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你比較特別
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在高興什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你來說是特別的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼覺得你說的是別的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你聊各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野沒有來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是跟Arcueid在約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙大概又因為貧血躺在床上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴你不高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這樣做真的沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說Roa也開始行動了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙只有晚上才活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是那麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看電影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很無聊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說的跟實際看的差別好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面暗暗的氣氛不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音很大卻不覺得吵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  最重要的是內容也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到人類能把虛構的故事發展到那種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很佩服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 你該不會是覺得很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不算是無聊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說很普通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇情真的很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那算很好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還有一堆更有趣的電影喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會有比剛剛更有趣的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是因為你在身邊我才會覺得有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是四線笛鯛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棲息在淺水珊瑚礁區域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是成群活動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃貝類或螃蟹時會游到海底
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道得挺清楚的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我從小就喜歡這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得很不可思議嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和自己想像不到的各種生物相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不像遇見吸血鬼那麼不可思議啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒想到會被人類殺死喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說會痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說我變了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我自己也不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個的關係真是不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不是吸血鬼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和志貴會變成什麼樣子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種假設的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很喜歡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種假設的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前只有在知識上瞭解這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從長眠中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得那個時候需要的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情結束之後就馬上沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以多告訴我一些關於你的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意我的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常常想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是吸血鬼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹你不高興了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你會吃漢堡之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到吸血鬼的食物應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴  你做得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說那種假設的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換志貴帶我去你想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你問我要去哪裡  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要去你的學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間應該沒有人在  不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我不是說過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid  我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼想到學校來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你一天大多數的時間不是都待在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度過什麼樣的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用什麼樣的表情歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道的時間裡的志貴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也在同樣的時光當中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:12:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很喜歡假設的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴你都在這裡做些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀書？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研讀歷史或是背公式和元素代號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼幫助嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定真的沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又為什麼要來？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們生存的時間很短
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有閒功夫去做這種事才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼沒有閒功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是機械
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要只考慮效率吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然花時間去做也許沒有用的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「沒有用」就真的那麼不好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有用又有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身懷那雙眼睛的力量活在世上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就表示你還有非做不可的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是活著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從8年前那場事故之後就一直這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我還是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一整天不也都是沒有用的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我就不太清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是變的不正常了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正常？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快樂、痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多餘的感情變得非常強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就叫作不正常嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會覺得快樂呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我以前從來沒有醒來這麼久過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會不會早就已經睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是作著自己胡思亂想的夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒過來志貴就不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的事情沒那麼容易瞭解的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等事情全部結束之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再約會一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再做一次沒有用的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡心盡力地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何義務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有任何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣約好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道部的活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道部？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說就是喝茶和學習茶藝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴也是茶道部的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  Ciel學姊有時候會請我喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了啊  突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了什麼讓你不高興的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Ciel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你跟她處不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  只聽到名字沒必要那麼生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel是教會的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教會？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們當成敵人的一群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久以前就認識學姊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不過是她讓你那麼認為而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會連我是誰也忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她為什麼要那麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她認為志貴是Roa的轉生目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是遠野家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊為什麼要追殺Roa？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是Roa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel過去曾是Roa的宿主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還做過殘酷的屠殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而殺死她的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是學姊不是還活著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是不會死而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來Ciel為了贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不斷追殺羅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的個性就是無法放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再讓我多當一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛管閒事的學姊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天被奇怪的傢伙攻擊時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel學姊救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然Ciel出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示可能是Roa嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是Roa的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能會沒有發現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是宿主的人格太強了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個什麼樣的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他全身都是繃帶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道關於…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  志貴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid Brunestud
